01:18:29,528 --> 01:18:32,496
And I need your help
to get my family back.
They are my family.

895
01:18:37,001 --> 01:18:39,503
That's for sleeping
with my wife...

896
01:18:39,538 --> 01:18:41,505
in the damn minivan.

897
01:18:42,006 --> 01:18:46,510
Your "yes" or "no" an...
your report has been timed out
or canceled at your request.

898
01:18:51,015 --> 01:18:53,482
It's him.

899
01:18:53,517 --> 01:18:56,020
Mr. Gibson, I believe
you have something of mine.

900
01:18:56,520 --> 01:18:58,988
Oh, no. I have
everything of yours.

901
01:18:59,023 --> 01:19:01,991
I have the syncording that
proves you are a clone.

902
01:19:02,026 --> 01:19:06,530
And I have everything
of yours... your family
in the palm of my hand.

903
01:19:06,565 --> 01:19:08,532
- Shall we trade?
- You read my mind.

904
01:19:08,567 --> 01:19:11,500
Just the highlights.
All right.

905
01:19:11,535 --> 01:19:17,041
I'll bring the disk
to the double x charter
office at 10:00 tonight.

906
01:19:17,076 --> 01:19:20,544
Be there with my family.

907
