Well, I had to stop you
from talking to the police.

909
01:19:32,091 --> 01:19:34,558
Yeah, that's a good one.

910
01:19:35,059 --> 01:19:40,029
That should do it.
What are you doing?

911
01:19:40,064 --> 01:19:43,532
Testing it.
Because I don't think you have
