915
01:20:03,087 --> 01:20:05,089
Let's try it.

916
01:20:17,601 --> 01:20:20,104
Wow!

917
01:20:23,107 --> 01:20:25,109
Cool.
Cool.

918
01:20:28,612 --> 01:20:31,080
You'd better be miles away
when this thing goes off.

919
01:20:31,115 --> 01:20:34,618
I'm more worried about
