927
01:20:59,143 --> 01:21:02,146
Don't start with "sorry."
Don't start! Don't start!
I am so sorry.

928
01:21:02,181 --> 01:21:04,613
Don't start with "sorry"!

929
01:21:04,648 --> 01:21:10,154
I know about the congenital
defects you've been embedding
into the clone D.N.A.

930
01:21:10,189 --> 01:21:13,157
There's my wife,
Johnny Phoenix and the others.

931
01:21:13,192 --> 01:21:16,160
But, Michael,
why my wife? Why?

932
01:21:16,195 --> 01:21:20,164
You're right, Griffin.

933
01:21:20,664 --> 01:21:24,168
It's a security protocol I
implemented. I didn't tell you
because you wouldn't understand.

934
01:21:24,203 --> 01:21:26,635
What should I understand?

935
01:21:26,670 --> 01:21:31,140
The only thing I understand
is that you gave my wife
cystic fibrosis.

936
01:21:31,175 --> 01:21:36,180
Griffin, calm down. Someone
made a mistake. This was never
meant to hurt Katherine.

937
01:21:36,215 --> 01:21:38,147
Oh, it didn't hurt her,
it just killed her.

938
01:21:38,182 --> 01:21:41,685
Suppose we clone a senator
who's agreed to support us
but he goes back on his word.

939
01:21:41,720 --> 01:21:44,153
What's the point?
Or Johnny Phoenix
wants to double his salary.

940
01:21:44,188 --> 01:21:47,691
By giving them shorter life
spans we guarantee our leverage.
What's the point?

941
01:21:47,726 --> 01:21:51,160
The point is...
if they betray us, they're dead.

942
01:21:51,195 --> 01:21:54,163
If they stay on the team,
we clone them again
and no harm done.

943
01:21:54,198 --> 01:21:57,201
And that's exactly what
we're gonna do with Katherine.
She's being cloned as we speak.

944
01:21:57,236 --> 01:22:01,705
- No, she's not. No.
- No, she's...

945
01:22:01,740 --> 01:22:04,673
Griffin, it was a mistake.

946
01:22:04,708 --> 01:22:09,213
If you're concerned about her
D.N.A., go through it yourself,
make sure it's clean.

947
01:22:09,248 --> 01:22:11,215
And obviously, there won't be
any charge for the cloning.

948
01:22:11,715 --> 01:22:14,683
Oh, no charge.
Thank you very much.

949
01:22:14,718 --> 01:22:17,721
