953
01:22:27,266 --> 01:22:29,698
I loved my wife very much.

954
01:22:29,733 --> 01:22:34,488
So much so that I promised
I would never bring her
back again, and I won't.

955
01:22:34,523 --> 01:22:39,243
If I can't bring her back again,
l’ll never bring back
anyone ever again.

956
01:22:40,744 --> 01:22:42,746
That's how much
I loved her.

957
01:22:44,748 --> 01:22:49,753
So it's over,
it's finished and I quit.

958
01:22:50,754 --> 01:22:52,721
Well, I can't let you quit.
Yeah, well.

959
01:22:52,756 --> 01:22:58,762
I've looked the other way
too often and l’ve justified
too much, so...

960
01:23:02,766 --> 01:23:06,270
l’m finished.
It's over.

961
01:23:09,273 --> 01:23:13,277
You know what l’m gonna do
for you, Griffin?
What are you gonna do for me?

962
01:23:13,312 --> 01:23:18,282
