the greatest gift that
you could possibly imagine.

963
01:23:18,317 --> 01:23:22,251
A gift?
I'm gonna save your life.
I'm gonna save Katherine.

964
01:23:22,286 --> 01:23:28,292
I'm gonna save our friendship.
And l’m gonna save
your marriage.

965
01:23:28,327 --> 01:23:30,794
Michael, what are you
talking about?

966
01:23:33,297 --> 01:23:38,802
I'm going to kill you now.
And then l’m going to clone you
using your latest syncording.

967
01:23:38,837 --> 01:23:42,806
Then l’m gonna clone Katherine
using her last syncording.
You understand?

968
01:23:43,307 --> 01:23:46,310
No.
Do you see
what l’m doing for you?

969
01:23:46,345 --> 01:23:49,278
You and Katherine
