970
01:23:49,313 --> 01:23:51,315
and neither one of you
will remember that you ever
promised not to clone her.

971
01:23:51,350 --> 01:23:53,782
Or that she even died.

972
01:23:53,817 --> 01:23:55,819
And obviously, you won't
remember this conversation.

973
01:24:05,329 --> 01:24:08,332
You're welcome.

974
01:24:28,852 --> 01:24:32,356
