978
01:25:37,456 --> 01:25:40,424
Come on.

979
01:25:51,935 --> 01:25:55,439
This is a private pad.
You can't land that here.
Replacement technologies only.

980
01:25:55,474 --> 01:25:58,442
I'm here to pick up
Mr. Drucker.

981
