985
01:26:17,496 --> 01:26:19,463
your pilot's on his way
down to reception.

986
01:26:22,466 --> 01:26:25,969
Now you listen to me.
Seal the building,
full security alert.

987
01:26:26,004 --> 01:26:28,972
You find this pilot.
