Okay, you did pretty good.

1001
01:27:53,557 --> 01:27:58,061
You fooled us at the airport.
You managed to turn
this place into a shambles.

1002
01:27:58,096 --> 01:28:02,566
- Want to make us come up there
and kill you? Fine.
- You're the greatest, dad.

1003
01:28:02,601 --> 01:28:06,069
But Mr. Drucker would like
to talk to you.

1004
01:28:06,104 --> 01:28:09,072
And of course
we do have your family.

1005
01:28:10,574 --> 01:28:13,542
All right.

1006
01:28:13,577 --> 01:28:15,579
Go get him, go get him.

1007
01:28:16,580 --> 01:28:19,082
[Door opens]
Well, well.

1008
01:28:21,084 --> 01:28:24,587
- Adam Gibson.
- I wish I could say,
"the one and only."

1009
01:28:24,622 --> 01:28:28,056
Looks like we both
went back on our word,
didn't we?

1010
01:28:28,091 --> 01:28:31,595
- You might find we have more
in common than you thought.
- Where's my family?

1011
01:28:31,630 --> 01:28:35,599
Right to business.
An admirable trait.

1012
01:28:38,602 --> 01:28:40,604
There they are.

1013
01:28:41,104 --> 01:28:43,572
- All safe and sound.
- For the moment.

1014
01:28:43,607 --> 01:28:48,111
And your syncording,
it's not on him.
It's not in his whispercraft.

1015
01:29:01,124 --> 01:29:05,128
I knew you'd
double-cross me,
so I gave it to my clone.

1016
01:29:05,163 --> 01:29:07,596
If anything happens
to me or my family,

1017
01:29:07,631 --> 01:29:12,636
the next time
you'll see your syncording
will be at your murder trial.

1018
01:29:12,671 --> 01:29:16,139
- Dr. Weir didn't
tell you, did he?
- Tell me what?

1019
01:29:17,641 --> 01:29:20,143
Adam, Adam, Adam.

1020
01:29:22,646 --> 01:29:25,649
He's not the clone.

1021
01:29:26,650 --> 01:29:29,152
You are.

1022
01:29:32,155 --> 01:29:34,157
I want you to ask
yourself something.

1023
01:29:34,658 --> 01:29:37,661
Do you remember anything after
being scanned by my bodyguard?

1024
01:29:37,696 --> 01:29:40,681
[Man #1]
I need to check your vision.
Look straight ahead.

1025
01:29:40,716 --> 01:29:43,693
Do you actually remember
changing places
with your friend?

1026
01:29:43,728 --> 01:29:46,635
[Man #2]
Hey, buddy, wake up.
We're here, woodland mall.

1027
01:29:46,670 --> 01:29:52,676
The salesman at the RePet shop
thought it was odd
that you came in twice...

1028
01:29:53,677 --> 01:29:56,179
asked the same
questions twice.

1029
01:29:56,680 --> 01:30:02,185
Still can't
make up your mind, huh?
You lost a dog, right?

1030
01:30:02,220 --> 01:30:07,691
[Hank's voice]
Let me see your chin.
You cut yourself shaving?

1031
01:30:08,692 --> 01:30:12,696
Your shaving cut?
Easily reproduced.

1032
01:30:14,698 --> 01:30:17,200
So was the scar
from your old war wound.

1033
01:30:19,703 --> 01:30:23,672
I know who I am.
I know you do.

1034
01:30:23,707 --> 01:30:27,210
Talia, how many times
have you been cloned?

1035
01:30:27,245 --> 01:30:30,714
I've lost count.
There's one way to tell.

1036
01:30:32,215 --> 01:30:35,684
Show him.

1037
01:30:35,719 --> 01:30:38,722
It's the only way
to keep track of what
generation a clone is.

1038
01:30:38,757 --> 01:30:43,727
See? Four dots means
she's been cloned
four times.

1039
01:30:43,762 --> 01:30:48,196
Come on. Let's
take a look at yours.

1040
01:30:48,231 --> 01:30:53,737
Come take a look in the mirror.
Let's find out if you are
who you think you are.

1041
01:31:00,744 --> 01:31:03,246
Just under
your left eye.

1042
01:31:15,759 --> 01:31:19,262
Kind of takes the fun
out of being alive,
doesn't it?

1043
01:31:20,764 --> 01:31:25,769
So you see, your family
is not really your family,
they're his.

1044
01:31:25,804 --> 01:31:30,774
And you, my friend,
are in exactly the same boat
as all of us.

1045
01:31:38,281 --> 01:31:43,787
If Adam Gibson gets that
syncording to the authorities,
we will all be destroyed.

1046
01:31:43,822 --> 01:31:49,292
If you really love
your wife and kid, you'll
tell me where Adam Gibson is.

1047
01:31:49,327 --> 01:31:53,261
We'll get my syncording back,
we'll get rid of him.

1048
01:31:53,296 --> 01:31:57,801
Tell me where Adam Gibson is.
We'll get my syncording back,
we'll get rid of him.

1049
01:31:57,836 --> 01:32:01,071
We'll get my syncording back,
we'll get rid of him.

1050
01:32:01,106 --> 01:32:04,307
And they'll never have to know
that you're the clone.

1051
01:32:05,809 --> 01:32:08,276
It's that or lose them forever.

1052
01:32:08,311 --> 01:32:12,315
You know, Adam. I'm not making
this offer because I have to.

1053
01:32:12,350 --> 01:32:14,783
I can get everything I need
from your memories.

1054
01:32:14,818 --> 01:32:19,823
The fact is, l’d like you
to understand you'd also
be serving a higher purpose.

1055
01:32:19,858 --> 01:32:24,845
