to get the laws changed.

1056
01:32:24,880 --> 01:32:30,109
And then we won't have to lose
our best people. We won't
have to lose our Mozarts.

1057
01:32:30,144 --> 01:32:35,338
We won't have to lose
our Martin Luther Kings.
We'll be able to conquer death.

1058
01:32:36,339 --> 01:32:39,843
We will finally
be able to conquer death.

1059
01:32:48,351 --> 01:32:53,857
And who gets to decide
who lives and who dies, you?

1060
01:32:54,357 --> 01:32:56,609
You have a better idea?

1061
01:32:56,644 --> 01:32:58,827
Yeah, what about god?

1062
01:32:58,862 --> 01:33:02,866
Oh, you're one of those.
I suppose you think science
is inherently evil.

1063
01:33:02,901 --> 01:33:08,872
No, I don't think
science is inherently evil.
But I think you are.

1064
01:33:08,907 --> 01:33:12,340
If you believe that god
created man in his own image,

1065
01:33:12,375 --> 01:33:15,378
then you also believe
that god gave man the power
to understand evolution.

1066
01:33:15,413 --> 01:33:18,882
To exploit science,
to manipulate the genetic code,

1067
01:33:18,917 --> 01:33:20,884
to do exactly what I am doing.

1068
01:33:21,384 --> 01:33:24,888
I'm just taking over
where god left off.

1069
01:33:27,891 --> 01:33:30,358
If you really believe that,

1070
01:33:30,393 --> 01:33:33,862
then you should clone yourself
while you're still alive.

1071
01:33:33,897 --> 01:33:37,901
And why is that?
So I can understand
your unique perspective?

1072
01:33:37,936 --> 01:33:42,405
No. So you can
go fuck yourself.

1073
01:33:47,410 --> 01:33:52,415
Now you're gonna
tell us where you put
Mr. Drucker's syncording!

1074
01:33:54,918 --> 01:34:00,423
