1088
01:35:11,529 --> 01:35:14,497
Keep this and wait here.
If l’m not back in an hour,

1089
01:35:14,532 --> 01:35:17,966
you know what to do.

1090
01:35:18,001 --> 01:35:21,004
Don't worry. Anything
happens to you or my family,

1091
01:35:21,039 --> 01:35:24,007
l’m gonna destroy
that son of a bitch.

1092
01:35:31,514 --> 01:35:33,982
You got the location?

1093
01:35:34,017 --> 01:35:38,021
The airport. I was just there.
