Let's go.

1094
01:35:38,521 --> 01:35:40,523
Betrayed by your own mind.

1095
01:35:52,035 --> 01:35:56,004
- Wait, wait!
- What?

1096
01:35:56,039 --> 01:35:58,006
They staged that scene
for our benefit.

1097
01:35:58,041 --> 01:36:01,544
The other one
was sitting behind him
so we couldn't see him. Look.

1098
01:36:01,579 --> 01:36:04,012
