his own syncording.

1099
01:36:04,047 --> 01:36:06,014
The other one was hiding
in the whispercraft...

1100
01:36:06,049 --> 01:36:09,302
and this one
avoided looking at him
so he wouldn't be in his memory.

1101
01:36:09,337 --> 01:36:12,698
- You mean the other one's
in this building too?
- Yes, that's correct.

1102
01:36:12,733 --> 01:36:16,059
Now, warn Vincent.
Put out another alert.
