Oh, god!

1112
01:37:29,299 --> 01:37:31,766
- Don't worry, sir.
Get him up.
- Oh, shit.

1113
01:37:31,801 --> 01:37:35,304
- Everything's okay now.
- I'm scared, dad.
I'm scared.

1114
01:37:35,339 --> 01:37:38,808
This isn't because
of the cigar?
No, l’ll explain later.

1115
01:37:39,309 --> 01:37:40,810
Dad, l’m scared.

1116
01:37:48,318 --> 01:37:51,821
Don't worry.
He's not going anywhere, sir.
We'll get him. Let's go.

1117
01:37:53,323 --> 01:37:57,327
Wait! Talia, you go.
You two stay here.

1118
01:37:59,329 --> 01:38:02,297
Have 'em block
all the exits.

1119
01:38:02,332 --> 01:38:07,837
Yeah, Henderson, come in.
Seal off the entire tank areas,
levels six and seven.

1120
01:38:12,342 --> 01:38:14,344
I'm trying, sir.
Give me a minute.

1121
01:38:14,844 --> 01:38:17,812
And get us some power
up here.

1122
01:38:17,847 --> 01:38:21,316
Don't move!
My daughter is right inside
that door.

1123
01:38:21,351 --> 01:38:24,854
Now, I don't want
to expose her
to any graphic violence.

1124
01:38:24,889 --> 01:38:27,357
She already gets enough
of that from the media.

1125
01:38:27,857 --> 01:38:31,611
Put your weapons down.
Nice and easy.

1126
01:38:31,646 --> 01:38:35,330
Good. Now, when
you go inside, you say...

1127
01:38:35,365 --> 01:38:37,867
have a nice flight.
Have a nice flight,
little girl.

1128
01:38:37,902 --> 01:38:39,869
Friends of daddy's.

1129
01:38:40,370 --> 01:38:42,372
All right, let's go.

1130
01:38:50,880 --> 01:38:54,384
Have a little midnight flight
with daddy and mommy.

1131
01:38:54,419 --> 01:38:57,387
There we are. All right?

1132
01:38:57,422 --> 01:38:59,354
Sorry.

1133
01:38:59,389 --> 01:39:01,391
There you go, sir.

1134
01:39:01,426 --> 01:39:04,161
Wiley. Go.

1135
01:39:04,196 --> 01:39:06,896
All right.

1136
01:39:07,397 --> 01:39:10,900
Wiley, just wait one second.

1137
01:39:19,409 --> 01:39:22,912
- Not again!
- [Wiley screams]

1138
01:39:23,913 --> 01:39:26,381
And don't
bring him back.

1139
01:39:26,416 --> 01:39:30,420
Stupid bastard blew a hole
through my stomach.

1140
01:39:30,455 --> 01:39:34,424
Oh, god!
I'll be dead
in 20 minutes tops.

1141
01:39:37,427 --> 01:39:39,929
But what better place,
right?

1142
01:39:39,964 --> 01:39:42,397
Henderson?
Where's my power?

1143
01:39:42,432 --> 01:39:44,899
Relays are coming
on-line now, sir.

1144
01:39:44,934 --> 01:39:48,438
[Henderson]
Get all exits blocked.
All exits!

1145
01:39:51,941 --> 01:39:53,943
Shit!

1146
01:39:58,448 --> 01:40:01,416
Go start warming up
a blank.

1147
01:40:01,451 --> 01:40:04,454
I want a fresh syncording.
I want my mind
to be up to the minute.

1148
01:40:55,004 --> 01:40:56,921
Okay, here it is.
This is a fresh one.

1149
01:40:56,956 --> 01:40:59,459
[Marshall]
This will be
a complete syncording.

1150
01:41:11,971 --> 01:41:13,973
- [Talia groaning]
- [Drucker]
Is that Talia?

1151
01:41:14,008 --> 01:41:16,976
[Talia]
Shit!
Go help her.

1152
01:41:17,011 --> 01:41:20,480
We'll find him.

1153
01:42:19,539 --> 01:42:23,042
What have you got?
Tanks three and four, nothing.

1154
01:42:23,077 --> 01:42:26,045
Okay, go.
Take the back walk.

1155
01:43:06,085 --> 01:43:08,588
- [Yelling]
- [Screaming]
- [Gunshot]

1156
01:43:15,094 --> 01:43:17,096
No!

1157
01:43:37,116 --> 01:43:40,119
No.

1158
01:43:47,627 --> 01:43:51,130
[Yells] oh, god!

1159
01:44:22,662 --> 01:44:24,664
[Gasps]

1160
01:44:32,171 --> 01:44:36,175
[Gasping]

1161
01:44:39,679 --> 01:44:42,181
Oh, no.

1162
01:45:02,201 --> 01:45:05,705
- Take her to your mother's.
Stay there until I pick you up.
- I got her.

1163
01:45:05,740 --> 01:45:07,672
Come with us, daddy.

1164
01:45:07,707 --> 01:45:10,710
I have to help a friend, okay?
Bye.

1165
01:45:10,745 --> 01:45:12,712
Love you.

1166
01:45:32,732 --> 01:45:36,235
- [Gasping]
- Wiley, you shot me!

1167
01:45:38,237 --> 01:45:41,240
Oh, right.
That was you.

1168
01:45:43,242 --> 01:45:46,245
I gotta get dressed.

1169
01:45:46,280 --> 01:45:48,713
[Groans]

1170
01:45:48,748 --> 01:45:53,252
You're not even gonna wait
until... I die?

1171
01:45:53,287 --> 01:45:58,758
Would you?
Come on, get it off.

1172
01:45:59,759 --> 01:46:02,762
Blood on the jacket.
Jesus Christ.

1173
01:46:17,276 --> 01:46:19,779
[Gasps, mutters]

1174
01:46:20,279 --> 01:46:21,781
What?

1175
01:46:23,783 --> 01:46:26,035
[Mumbles]

1176
01:46:26,070 --> 01:46:28,252
What?

1177
01:46:28,287 --> 01:46:30,289
- [Gasps]
- What?

1178
01:46:36,295 --> 01:46:41,300
Look. Adam,
we can make a deal.

1179
01:46:41,801 --> 01:46:46,305
You have absolutely no reason
to kill me. I didn't do anything
to you. It was all him.

1180
01:46:46,806 --> 01:46:50,810
Listen to me.
I can rebuild all of this
in a very short time.

1181
01:46:50,845 --> 01:46:53,778
I can still save you, Adam.
Save me?

1182
01:46:53,813 --> 01:46:58,317
We put congenital defects
into the clone D.N.A. to give
the clones short life spans.

1183
01:46:58,352 --> 01:47:01,821
You want to know what
you're gonna die of?
How long you've got to live?

1184
01:47:01,856 --> 01:47:04,323
We can go right upstairs,
right now,
and look it up.

1185
01:47:40,359 --> 01:47:42,862
We all have to die someday.

1186
01:47:42,897 --> 01:47:45,329
We don't have to die.

1187
01:47:45,364 --> 01:47:48,367
I'm offering you the chance
to live forever.

1188
01:47:48,868 --> 01:47:52,371
Never aging.
Perfect in every way.

1189
01:47:52,406 --> 01:47:54,874
Perfect?
Like you?

1190
01:47:55,875 --> 01:47:58,878
Look!
Here is your perfection!

1191
01:47:58,913 --> 01:48:01,846
No.

1192
01:48:01,881 --> 01:48:06,851
No. No. No.

1193
01:48:06,886 --> 01:48:10,389
Oh, god.
Oh, god.

1194
01:48:12,391 --> 01:48:16,360
There's no need
to panic.
I can fix this.

1195
01:48:16,395 --> 01:48:20,900
No, you won't fix anything.
It's over. It's finished.
It's finished!

1196
01:48:21,400 --> 01:48:23,903
[Groans]

1197
01:48:28,407 --> 01:48:30,910
[Groans]

1198
01:48:39,919 --> 01:48:45,424
When I said you should
screw yourself, I didn't mean
for you to take it literally.

1199
01:49:14,453 --> 01:49:19,959
Go after him.
Just get him.

1200
01:49:23,462 --> 01:49:25,464
[Security guard]
Check the roof.
You, you, up top!

1201
01:49:46,986 --> 01:49:50,489
[Guard]
He's goin' up!
He's goin' up the stairs!

1202
01:50:41,040 --> 01:50:42,541
Come on!

1203
01:51:06,065 --> 01:51:08,567
- Can you fly this?
- Better than you can.

1204
01:51:08,602 --> 01:51:11,570
Good. Because
your shooting sucks.

1205
01:51:20,079 --> 01:51:22,581
Let's get out of here.

1206
01:52:04,123 --> 01:52:07,126
[Glass cracking]

1207
01:52:10,129 --> 01:52:14,383
[Yelling]

1208
01:52:14,418 --> 01:52:18,637
[Yelling]

1209
01:52:24,610 --> 01:52:26,645
Oh, shit!

1210
01:52:35,154 --> 01:52:38,657
Come on! Come on!

1211
01:52:58,677 --> 01:53:01,180
Try to climb over me!

1212
01:53:10,189 --> 01:53:12,691
Come on! Hurry up!

1213
01:53:14,693 --> 01:53:16,695
Shit!

1214
01:53:22,701 --> 01:53:24,203
Come on!

1215
01:53:45,724 --> 01:53:47,726
Oh, shit!

1216
01:54:13,252 --> 01:54:15,719
You know, I keep wondering.

1217
01:54:15,754 --> 01:54:19,257
Am I really human?
Do I have a soul?

1218
01:54:19,292 --> 01:54:22,761
Well, your D.N.A. scan
came back normal.

1219
01:54:22,796 --> 01:54:24,728
Didn't it?
Yeah.

1220
01:54:24,763 --> 01:54:28,732
Zero defects.
Just like a RePet commercial.

1221
01:54:28,767 --> 01:54:31,770
Well, if you're not human,
don't you think
they would've mentioned it?

1222
01:54:34,773 --> 01:54:38,242
All right, enough philosophy.

1223
01:54:38,277 --> 01:54:41,280
I better get going.
I got three weeks at sea
to figure that out.

1224
01:54:41,780 --> 01:54:44,248
You have to hurry
if you want to see Clara.

1225
01:54:44,283 --> 01:54:47,786
Oh, thanks for letting me
say good-bye to your family.

1226
01:54:47,821 --> 01:54:52,291
Now, wait.
This is your family too.

1227
01:54:52,791 --> 01:54:55,759
You were willing to die
to save them.

1228
01:54:55,794 --> 01:55:00,799
Think about that while
you're out at sea wondering
if you're really human or not.

1229
01:55:00,834 --> 01:55:04,803
Because if that's
not being human,
I don't know what is.

1230
01:55:06,805 --> 01:55:09,308
Thanks.

1231
01:55:14,313 --> 01:55:16,280
Hello, everybody.

1232
01:55:16,315 --> 01:55:19,318
Look what I brought.
A kitty!

1233
01:55:22,321 --> 01:55:25,289
Oh, Sadie. Oh.

1234
01:55:25,324 --> 01:55:29,328
I thought that, um,
Hank's cat was...
she is.

1235
01:55:29,363 --> 01:55:31,848
But you hate RePets.

1236
01:55:31,883 --> 01:55:34,333
Well, I changed my mind.

1237
01:55:34,368 --> 01:55:36,300
You old softie.

1238
01:55:36,335 --> 01:55:40,304
Can we keep her?
Please? Please?
Of course.

1239
01:55:40,339 --> 01:55:44,343
That's why I brought her home.
Put her down. Good.

1240
